result.name: 漢和韓國料理-觀塘店

reviews.text: Large variety of food to pick from. The meat is well marinated, the vegetables are decently fresh along with the fruits and the desserts are pretty good. The buffet also includes drinks such as Coca cola, Fanta and milkis. There is also food that are already cooked you can pick from. However the desserts are a bit too sweet for me. The  service is pretty friendly. The price is reasonable, which is 133$ per person with an extra 10% service charge. For elders or children it is 113$.
Good food for decent price

Yes they serve hot plated Korean meat with rice which is one of my favorite lunch place. Hotpot is also served but not tried yet. My favorite dish is Korean BBQ lamb with rice.

The shop is spacious and it is not difficult to find a seat during weekdays lunch hours. The price is around HKD45-58 for lunch set.
Bad food Quality
A fair choice for lunch barbeque buffet. Good food quality and variety, good services. Good place for gathering with friends.

reviews.text: 平靚正！唔會歧視單人加額外收費！要彈嘅係海產類很少！高價貨冇！
經濟實惠，食物款式多，質數好。長者有優惠$30。
食物質素差，一點也不值二百幾元，不建議浪費時間去食。

Large variety of food to pick from. The meat is well marinated, the vegetables are decently fresh along with the fruits and the desserts are pretty good. The buffet also includes drinks such as Coca cola, Fanta and milkis. There is also food that are already cooked you can pick from. However the desserts are a bit too sweet for me. The  service is pretty friendly. The price is reasonable, which is 133$ per person with an extra 10% service charge. For elders or children it is 113$.
很划算，食物很豐富!  場地夠大和舒適!  我會再光顧!
